ce]] \u2013 ''Senior (6'0, 170)''\n*43  Parker Bearden \u2013 ''Sophomore (6'1, 201)'' \n*45  Bo Grant \u2013 ''Senior (6'2, 201)''\n\n'''Long Snappers'''\n*45  Thomas Fletcher \u2013 ''Freshman (6'2, 220)''\n*52  Scott Meyer \u2013 ''[[File:Redshirt.svg|10px|Redshirt]] Freshman (6'2, 226)''\n*53  Ryan Parris \u2013 ''Junior (6'0, 209)''\n\n|-\n|colspan=\"7\"|<hr />\n*<small>: 2017 Alabama Crimson Tide Football Commits (08/05/2016)</small>\n|}\n\n====Depth chart====\nAs of the Crimson Tide's opening game against Florida State:<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.al.com/alabamafootball/2017/08/alabama_releases_first_2017_de.html|title=Alabama releases first 2017 depth chart|date=August 28, 2017|website=AL.com}}</ref>\n{{CFB Team Depth Chart\n| OScheme       = Single Set Back\n| DScheme       = 3-4\n| SpecialTeams  = Yes\n| KeyReserves   = No\n| 3Deep         = Yes\n| QB_Starter    = [[Jalen Hurts]]\n| QB_Backup     = [[Tua Tagovailoa]]\n| QB_Third      = \n| RB1_Starter   = [[Damien Harris]]\n| RB1_Backup    = [[Bo Scarbrough]]\n| RB1_Third     = [[Josh Jacobs]]\n| RB1_Fourth    = [[Najee Harris]]\n| FB_Starter    = \n| FB_Backup     = \n| FB_Third      = \n| WR1_Starter   = [[Calvin Ridley]] \n| WR1_Backup    = [[Henry Ruggs III]]\n| WR1_Third     = Derek Kief\n| WR2_Starter   = [[Robert Foster (American football)|Robert Foster]]\n| WR2_Backup    = [[DeVonta Smith]]\n| WR2_Third     = \n| WR3_Starter   = [[Cam Sims]]\n| WR3_Backup    = [[Jerry Jeudy]]\n| WR3_Third     = Xavian Marks\n| WR4_Starter   = \n| WR4_Backup = \n| WR4_Third =\n| TE1_Starter   = [[Hale Hentges]]\n| TE1_Backup    = [[Irv Smith Jr.]]\n| TE1_Third     = Miller Forristall\n| LT_Starter    = [[Jonah Williams]]\n| LT_Backup     = [[Alex Leatherwood]]\n| LT_Third      = \n| LG_Starter    = [[Ross Pierschbacher]]\n| LG_Backup     = Josh Casher\n| LG_Third      = Dallas Warmack\n| C_Starter     = [[Bradley Bozeman]]\n| C_Backup      = Brandon Kennedy\n| C_Third       = \n| RG_Starter    = Lester Cotton\n| 