dschaft''\n* 2014: ''[[The Breakup Guru]]''\n* 2014: ''[[Gone with the Bullets]]''\n* 2014: ''[[The Hunger Games: Mockingjay \u2013 Part 1]]''\n* 2014: ''Impossible''\n* 2015: ''[[Furious 7]]''\n* 2015: ''[[Wolf Totem (film)|Wolf Totem]]''\n* 2015: ''[[Zhong Kui: Snow Girl and the Dark Crystal]]''\n* 2015: ''[[Fantastic Four (2015 film)|Fantastic Four]]''\n* 2015: ''[[Bridge of Spies (film)|Bridge of Spies]]''\n* 2017: ''[[Wonder Woman (2017 film)|Wonder Woman]]''\n* 2017: ''[[Skyhunter]]''\n* 2017: ''[[Power Rangers (film)|Power Rangers]]''\n* 2017: ''[[The Girl in the Spider's Web]]''\n* 2018: ''[[Overlord (2018 film)|Overlord]]''\n* 2018: ''[[Mary Poppins Returns]]''\n* 2018: ''[[Help I shrunk my Parents!]]''\n* 2018: ''[[Goosebumps 2 (2018 film)|Goosebumps 2]]''\n* 2019: ''[[Child's Play (2019 film)|Child's Play]]''\n* 2019: ''[[Midway (2019 film)|Midway]]''\n* 2019: ''[[Iron Sky: The Coming Race (2019 film)|Iron Sky: The Coming Race]]''\n* 2019: ''[[The Wandering Earth (2019 film)|The Wandering Earth]]''\n* 2019: ''[[4 Zauberhafte Schwestern (2019 film)|4 Zauberhafte Schwestern]]''\n* 2019: ''[[A Dog's Way Home (2019 film)|A Dog's<ref><ref></ref></ref> Way Home]]''\n* 2020: ''[[Lassie Come Home (2020 film)|Lassie Come Home ]]''\n{{colend}}\n\n=== TV shows ===\n{{colbegin}}\n* 2008: ''[[Fringe (TV series)|Fringe]]'' ([[Fringe (season 1)|season 1]], episodes 1,3,5,6)\n* 2010: ''[[Outsourced (TV series)|Outsourced]]''\n* 2010: ''[[Undercovers (2010 TV series)|Undercovers]]'' (episodes 1,3,5,6)\n* 2011: ''[[Terra Nova (TV series)|Terra Nova]]''\n* 2011: ''[[Hawaii Five-O (1968 TV series)|Hawaii Five-O]]'' ([[Hawaii Five-O (1968 TV series, season 2)|season 2]], episodes 1-13)\n* 2011: ''[[Grimm (TV series)|Grimm]]'' ([[Grimm (season 1)|season 1]], episodes 1-9)\n* 2012: ''[[Revolution (TV series)|Revolution]]''\n* 2012: ''[[Go On (TV series)|Go On]]''\n* 2012: ''[[The Mindy Project]]''\n* 2012\u20132019: ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' (since [[Game of Thrones (season 2)|se